c:
1st week of July, we finished a motivating Eco-design Workshop in collaboration with the specialized environmental consultancy inèdit.

&nbsp;

Throughout two sessions, the cross-functional team from DOGA reviewed the forth-coming and applicable legislations regarding Eco-design and their impact on DOGA products.

They also had the opportunity to analyse the DOGA Product Life Cycle, identifying the most critical issues.

&nbsp;

This training initiative is designed to integrate environmental criteria into every stage of product development, promoting a more conscious design culture aligned with today’s industrial challenges.

&nbsp;

At DOGA, we continue moving forward toward a more sustainable, innovative, and responsible company!🌍🌱

&nbsp;

